{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-009", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·009.1", "text_original": "摽有梅，其實七兮，求我庶士，迨其吉兮。", "text_normalized": "摽有梅，其實七兮，求我庶士，迨其吉兮。", "notes": "摽有梅 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-009", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·009.2", "text_original": "摽有梅，其實三兮，求我庶士，迨其今兮。", "text_normalized": "摽有梅，其實三兮，求我庶士，迨其今兮。", "notes": "摽有梅 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-009__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-009", "source_id": "guofeng-zhaonan-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·召南·009.3", "text_original": "摽有梅，頃筐塈之，求我庶士，迨其謂之。", "text_normalized": "摽有梅，頃筐塈之，求我庶士，迨其謂之。", "notes": "摽有梅 Chinese stanza 3."}
